<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to MyTrackr</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f5; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .header { background-color: #101828; color: #ffffff; padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center; }
        .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0; }
        .content { padding: 40px; color: #344054; line-height: 1.6; }
        .footer { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 20px 40px; text-align: center; color: #667085; font-size: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #eaecf0; }
        h1 { color: #101828; margin-top: 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2 class="logo">MyTrackr</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Welcome aboard, {{name}}!</h1>
            <p>We're thrilled to have you join MyTrackr. You are now equipped to take complete control of your financial tracking and business operations.</p>
            <p>With MyTrackr, you can seamlessly connect your bank accounts, categorize transactions, generate tax estimates, and monitor your business health instantly.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions or run into any issues, just hit reply to this email, and our team will be right there with you.</p>
            <br>
            <p>Cheers,<br>The MyTrackr Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 MyTrackr. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
